# Repo-root Docker build context exclusions.
# This governs the PROCESSOR image build (the only one that uses repo root as
# context, because it embeds schemas/redaction/patterns.yaml via include_str!).
# Keeps the context lean — excludes build artifacts, deps, and VCS.

.git
.github
**/node_modules
**/target
**/dist
**/.next
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.log
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
assets/
*.bundle
.DS_Store
